Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for feature representation and explores the applicability of their method for performing spatial transformations and predicting future latent vectors of a video sequence. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a Variational Autoencoder and a novel controller module suggests that the paper may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the exploration of the applicability of their method for video sequences suggests that the paper may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
